user_query: Hello! How can I assist you today?
I need help with my account.
Sure, I can help with that. What seems to be the problem?
I forgot my password and can't log in.
No worries, I can help you reset your password.
Please click on the 'Forgot Password' link on the login page.
I did that, but I didn't receive any email.
Have you checked your spam folder?
Yes, I checked everywhere.
Let me verify your email address. What is your email?
It's user@example.com.
Thank you. I will resend the password reset email.
Please check your inbox now.
I got the email. Thank you!
You're welcome! Is there anything else I can help you with?
No, that's all for now. Thanks!
Have a great day!
Hi, I need help with my order.
Sure, can you provide your order number?
Thank you. Let me check the status of your order.
Your order is on the way and should arrive by tomorrow.
Great, thank you!
